ID  - 35511085
T1  - Intrafollicular Concentrations of the Oocyte-secreted Factors GDF9 and BMP15 Vary Inversely in Polycystic Ovaries.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1210/clinem/dgac272
A1  - Kristensen, Stine Gry
A1  - Kumar, Ajay
A1  - Mamsen, Linn Salto
A1  - Kalra, Bhanu
A1  - Pors, Susanne Elisabeth
A1  - Botkjaer, Jane Alro
A1  - Macklon, Kirsten Tryde
A1  - Fedder, Jens
