T1  - Genome-wide association study meta-analysis identifies three novel loci for circulating anti-Mullerian hormone levels in women.
T3  - Update of: medRxiv. 2020 Nov 03:2020.10.29.20221390. doi: 10.1101/2020.10.29.20221390 PMID: 33173903 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/33173903] Comment in: Endocrine. 2023 Aug;81(2):388-389. doi: 10.1007/s12020-023-03380-0 PMID: 37115376 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/37115376] Comment in: Front Endocrinol (Lausanne). 2024 Jan 09;14:1282056. doi: 10.3389/fendo.2023.1282056 PMID: 38264282 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/38264282]
