T1  - Association of body mass index with serum anti-Mullerian hormone and inhibin B levels among 8323 women attending a reproductive medical center: a cross-sectional study.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s12020-021-02839-2
A1  - Wang, Yaqi
A1  - Wu, Li
A1  - Yang, Zhengyu
A1  - Xu, Ruijun
A1  - Duan, Yonggang
A1  - Lin, Jiajia
A1  - Cui, Xiuqing
