T1  - Physical Exercise following bariatric surgery in women with Morbid obesity: Study protocol clinical trial (SPIRIT compliant).
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1097/MD.0000000000019427
A1  - Soriano-Maldonado, Alberto
