T1  - Circulating antimullerian hormone and steroid hormone levels remain high in pregnant women with polycystic ovary syndrome at term.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2018.11.028
A1  - Piltonen, Terhi T
A1  - Giacobini, Paolo
A1  - Edvinsson, Asa
